{"tid":1779240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Times]咪撚再屈手足係輸打贏要先屌條女","createTime":"2019-12-11T14:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T16:57:14.000Z","uid":95520,"like":75,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e4b91d468ac6cf04a3d47267c032efa48ef01f14","tid":1779240,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T14:01:02.000Z","msg":"因為輸而留言嘅我只係見到係話可惜<br />\n無見人係因為自己無得贏而屌<br />\n<br />\n成班無知撚可唔可以留意多啲世界發生緊咩事<br />\n好老老柒柒講句我根本完全唔care呢條線<br />\n亦唔好諗住屈我毛<br />\n呢條女一開始出嚟我已經屌鳩緊佢<br />\n全世界都屌緊呢條女嘅時候都仲要屈手足係輸撚贏要真係好撚肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n留意吓呢條女嘅事蹟先啦<br />\n佢日常嘅碳排放仲多過我同你啊<br />\n更何況而家都只係喺連登圍內用廣東話屌都要比你哋用啲咁難聽嘅說話訓示"},{"pid":"1ffb27d8d30d220718fbe71c0686940f9683aedc","tid":1779240,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T14:02:04.000Z","msg":"努力打好國際線<br />\n今日香港都成為美加焦點<br />\n<br />\n 【Twitter要人!!】美加議員人權日tweet集合list!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1779138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1779138</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">需要人入去推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Twitter 需要大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"eca7c7d1afd5705aaa6b1d516ffe45694e0b9f07","tid":1779240,"uid":95520,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T14:02:07.000Z","msg":"屌晒你哋老母"},{"pid":"881528e09e6d5b1d1f20751b253fb7573a42a604","tid":1779240,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T14:02:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0475691bdce0a39815d066dc2adbc6f95b85de0d","tid":1779240,"uid":28558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T14:0